{
  "id": "rules_glossary/s/spiritspeaking",
  "lookup_group": "rules_glossary",
  "lookup_id": "spiritspeaking",
  "title": "Spiritspeaking",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Spirit Speakers"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/s/spirit_speaker_specialty",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/S/spirit_speaker"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "are adept at interacting with beings in the spirit realm, but to do so, they must first enter the trance-like state known as \u201cspiritspeaking.\u201d When a Ranger does this, they gain the ability to interact with spirit beings. In this state they can also influence the physical world in ways they could not previously."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When an ability instructs you to spiritspeak,"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "exhaust"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/e/exhaust",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/E/exhaust"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "your"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "role"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/r/role",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/role"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "and replace your"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Common Tests"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/c/common_test",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/common_tests"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "card with the Spirit Speaker Tests card. While you are spiritspeaking:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "li",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You no longer have access to"
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "common tests"
                }
              ],
              "id": "rules_glossary/c/common_test",
              "anchor": "",
              "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/common_tests"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "li",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You cannot perform any"
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "tests"
                }
              ],
              "id": "rules_glossary/t/tests",
              "anchor": "",
              "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/tests"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "that are not printed on, or used to interact with, a spirit."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "li",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can perform any of the"
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "tests"
                }
              ],
              "id": "rules_glossary/t/tests",
              "anchor": "",
              "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/tests"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "on the Spirit Speaker Tests card (the Influence test can be used on any type of being, not just Spirits)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When you"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "ready"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/r/ready",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/ready"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "your"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "role"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/r/role",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/role"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "(either during the"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "refresh phase"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/p/phase_4_refresh",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/P/phase_4_refresh"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "or due to another effect), you stop spiritspeaking. Replace your Spirit Speaker Tests card with the"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Common Tests"
            }
          ],
          "id": "rules_glossary/c/common_test",
          "anchor": "",
          "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/common_tests"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "card."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note: The Descendant of the Guide"
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "role"
                }
              ],
              "id": "rules_glossary/r/role",
              "anchor": "",
              "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/role"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "does not instruct you to spiritspeak when it is"
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "exhausted"
                }
              ],
              "id": "rules_glossary/e/exhaust",
              "anchor": "",
              "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/E/exhaust"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Instead, it instructs you to perform a single"
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "test"
                }
              ],
              "id": "rules_glossary/t/tests",
              "anchor": "",
              "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/tests"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "from the Spirit Speaker Test card."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "items": [],
  "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/S/spiritspeaking"
}